name: Tru Dhillon
text: This Pizzahut has reminded me why I do not order Pizzahut... I waited close to an hour for my initial order of pasta and bread sticks. Well.. I never got the bread sticks or a fork for my pasta and I am in a hotel room with no silverware. …More

name: Jrock Nemo
text: I got a message pizza is out for delivery 21-31 min away. I had to call the 55 minutes  after the text to ask about my pizza. I never got my delivery  very bad service the pizza is good pizza hut  is good but the service is horrible!!!

Has impeccable,  neh perfect  customer service  skills. New favorite pizza hut in the county because of here. Pizza was good too!

name: Moses Mobeta
text: I love it , thank you buddies for putting together a delicious calzone.

name: Suzanne Mitchell
text: Worst customer service.  Did not get the order that was placed and then no one answers the phone, just put you on hold for 28 min and then hang up.  Complete morons.

name: Chris robert
text: Why have a phone number if you are not going to answer it.

name: Brandon Sichting
text: Pizza was as usual. Good service. I can only assume that the bread sticks are pre-made and set for a few hours before they sale them because they were rock hard and could not eat them. Overall not a horrible Pizza Hut.

name: JR Curley
text: This is a very small Pizza Hut, made primarily for pick-up and delivery. The location is a bit run down, and is at the north end of a small restaurant cluster, making parking challenging at times. Delivery speeds are good, and pick up is smooth. Staff are friendly, jovial and active.

name: June Daye
text: Every now and then they try to come up with something new, it never works for me. I rather stay with their good old Pizza. It usually do the work.

name: Johnna Carter
text: Visiting Manhattan Beach area and needed quick bite for the kiddos, pizza  and service was great!! Will be back.

name: Ryan Patel
text: Super good pizza and I was surprised by the fast service!

name: Caleb Sturges
text: Absolutely terrible service. I mean bad even for pizza hut. The people here barely speak english and they mess up your order. I just ordered a half hour ago and after waiting all this time they gave my order to someone else. Now I have to wait for them to remake the whole thing.

name: Cheryl Murphy
text: service needs a little improvement.

name: Sallia Goldstein
text: It's pizza hut. You shouldn't be expecting a state of the art gourmet meal dude.
